02:00:18.240 --> 02:00:20.880
It was a frightful place to be going to.

02:00:20.880 --> 02:00:21.880
Yes.

02:00:21.880 --> 02:00:26.880
You're not exactly inconspicuous.

02:00:26.880 --> 02:00:41.080
Well, you know, I was invited years later to the McDonald's High School All-Star

02:00:41.080 --> 02:00:47.080
Game, okay, in Indiana.

02:00:47.080 --> 02:00:52.080
And so I went there and I had a good time.

02:00:52.080 --> 02:00:58.080
And after I spoke, they asked me to take pictures.

02:00:58.080 --> 02:01:02.080
I'll picture with each one of the participants.

02:01:02.080 --> 02:01:03.080
Boys and girls.

02:01:03.080 --> 02:01:04.080
It was two games.

02:01:04.080 --> 02:01:08.080
A boys and two game and a girls game.

02:01:08.080 --> 02:01:18.080
So while the female high school player of the year was a young lady from Colorado.

02:01:18.080 --> 02:01:27.680
And so she was while I said the picture up, she says, Mr. Russell, I like to say something to you.

02:01:27.680 --> 02:01:32.080
You said something to that in your speech that I would carry with me for the rest of my

02:01:32.080 --> 02:01:36.080
life.

02:01:36.080 --> 02:01:38.080
What?

02:01:38.080 --> 02:01:47.080
She said to us, do not be afraid.

02:01:47.080 --> 02:01:58.080
Because all decisions made out of fear are usually bad decisions.

02:01:58.080 --> 02:02:05.080
And you're going to a new world from high school to college, into college, into the world.

02:02:05.080 --> 02:02:08.080
Do not be afraid.

02:02:08.080 --> 02:02:09.080
Because you're all right.

02:02:09.080 --> 02:02:15.080
You got this far?

02:02:15.080 --> 02:02:17.080
Do not be afraid.

02:02:17.080 --> 02:02:28.080
Well, I may be not too bright, but I cannot recall the rest of how I was afraid.

02:02:28.080 --> 02:02:38.080
I would be shy to live in.

02:02:38.080 --> 02:02:48.080
Every time I could do something, I see it as an opportunity.

02:02:48.080 --> 02:02:54.080
Could you tell me a little bit about your relationships with other civil rights figures from that

02:02:54.080 --> 02:02:58.080
area that you have a neat Malcolm X or Martin Luther King?

