02:03:06.080 --> 02:03:14.080
I know Louis Farricot.

02:03:14.080 --> 02:03:18.080
He's been to a house a few times.

02:03:18.080 --> 02:03:24.080
He came out with...

02:03:24.080 --> 02:03:27.080
Before he changed his mind, he was cash his claim.

02:03:27.080 --> 02:03:32.080
And the reason cash was covered by house was...

02:03:32.080 --> 02:03:36.080
I was a gold medal winner in the 56 Olympics.

02:03:36.080 --> 02:03:43.080
And I always had affection for gold medal winners.

02:03:43.080 --> 02:03:53.080
Because I knew what it takes.

02:03:53.080 --> 02:03:56.080
And so I knew the last...

02:03:56.080 --> 02:03:58.080
Much of Washington.

02:03:58.080 --> 02:04:05.080
I stayed the same hotel as Reverend Martin Luther King.

02:04:05.080 --> 02:04:10.080
And so we met in lobby and had a brief conversation.

02:04:10.080 --> 02:04:14.080
And I told him I was there for the march.

02:04:14.080 --> 02:04:22.080
And he invited me to gold stage with what he made a big speech.

02:04:22.080 --> 02:04:26.080
And I respectfully declined.

02:04:26.080 --> 02:04:37.080
And the reason I declined was they had worked for a couple of years to put their thing together.

02:04:37.080 --> 02:04:41.080
And I hadn't done anything.

02:04:41.080 --> 02:04:43.080
And it would not be right.

02:04:43.080 --> 02:04:45.080
I didn't think...

02:04:45.080 --> 02:04:49.080
For a mean gold stage and say, hey listen, this is what we've done.

02:04:49.080 --> 02:04:54.080
And I hadn't done anything.

02:04:54.080 --> 02:04:58.080
So I said the first role.

02:04:58.080 --> 02:05:04.080
I had enjoyed it, but I didn't want to be one of those guys.

02:05:04.080 --> 02:05:06.080
Hey look at me.

