02:05:18.080 --> 02:05:20.080
I'd love to see that.

02:05:20.080 --> 02:05:22.080
I don't think so.

02:05:22.080 --> 02:05:24.080
I was just one of the guys.

02:05:24.080 --> 02:05:28.080
I was one of the people.

02:05:28.080 --> 02:05:30.080
They're to support that.

02:05:30.080 --> 02:05:36.080
And when he was killed that's during the season and your next the last year I guess.

02:05:36.080 --> 02:05:42.080
