02:05:58.080 --> 02:06:06.080
Now we think it would be a bad thing for the city of Philadelphia.

02:06:06.080 --> 02:06:16.080
If we call the game off and you got 12 or 13,000 people on the great stress.

02:06:16.080 --> 02:06:19.080
And really, really annoyed.

02:06:19.080 --> 02:06:22.080
That's a quiet way of putting it.

02:06:22.080 --> 02:06:25.080
On the streets.

02:06:25.080 --> 02:06:34.080
And so we said, well, we'll do is we play the game and we keep these 12 or 13,000 people in the game in time to cool off.

02:06:34.080 --> 02:06:37.080
So that you don't have riots in the street.

02:06:37.080 --> 02:06:39.080
That's the reason we played that game.

02:06:39.080 --> 02:06:43.080
Then we didn't play for a week or so.

02:06:43.080 --> 02:06:52.080
But we do some things we thought about.

02:06:52.080 --> 02:06:55.080
Did you know I'll leave much after you?

02:06:55.080 --> 02:07:03.080
When you said, oh, yeah, I do him when he was a kid boxer.

