Of course, to reach the top of your field.

02:07:14.080 --> 02:07:21.080
It takes more than physical ability.

02:07:21.080 --> 02:07:32.080
You have to know what you're doing to get to the top of your field no matter what the field.

02:07:32.080 --> 02:07:40.080
Because there are things you have to do to execute what it takes to be the top of your field.

02:07:40.080 --> 02:07:51.080
And so, our lead was not only a great, great boxer.

02:07:51.080 --> 02:08:02.080
But he's a psychologist and a brave, brave man.

02:08:02.080 --> 02:08:10.080
I was in Boston with the guy says, I want you to disobey Muhammad Ali.

